  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    A letter from Rishi Sunak to Sir David Norgrove on the date of the government and UK Statistics Authority’s response to their joint consultation on reform to the Retail Prices Index
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A letter from the Chancellor to the Chair of the UK Statistics Authority (UKSA) Board announcing that the government and UKSA’s response to their joint consultation on reform to the Retail Prices Index will be published alongside the Spending Review on 25 November.</p>

  </div>
</div>

